---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Find Flight Training Resources | Flight School Friend"
  description="Research the people, schools, and resources that may shape your flight training path. Template previews for now."
>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Find Flight Training Resources</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4 leading-relaxed">Research the people, schools, and resources that may shape your flight training path.</p>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">These directory pages are template previews for now. Use them to understand what to compare, what to verify, and what to ask before choosing a provider.</p>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-xl text-lg transition shadow-md">Start Here</a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <a href="/find/flight-schools/" class="block bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm">
        <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Template Preview</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Flight Schools</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Compare flight schools by training structure, aircraft availability, instructor fit, scheduling, pricing transparency, and student goal fit.</p>
        <span class="text-slate-700 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Preview Template &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/find/ame/" class="block bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm">
        <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Template Preview</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Aviation Medical Examiners</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Plan your medical certification research and learn what to clarify before you spend heavily on training.</p>
        <span class="text-slate-700 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Preview Template &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/find/scholarships/" class="block bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm">
        <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Template Preview</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Scholarships</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Explore scholarship research categories and build a list of possible funding opportunities.</p>
        <span class="text-slate-700 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Preview Template &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/find/cfi-dpe/" class="block bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm">
        <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Template Preview</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">CFI / DPE</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Understand how instructors and examiners fit into the training process, and what to ask as you prepare.</p>
        <span class="text-slate-700 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Preview Template &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Before you contact a school</h2>
      <ul class="text-left text-slate-300 space-y-3 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm">
        {[
          'Know your goal: hobby, career, travel, ownership, or research-first',
          'Estimate your realistic budget',
          'Clarify medical readiness if needed',
          'Compare at least 2–3 providers',
          'Ask about aircraft availability and instructor scheduling',
          'Understand refund, cancellation, and payment policies',
          'Avoid committing to a large package before you understand the fit',
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sky-500 font-bold">✓</span> {item}</li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition">Take the Flight School Decision Tool</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
